OL,3,CFour-nation summit needed now to
OL,4,Ctackle child poverty, says Stephen
OL,5,CFlynn
OL,7,FSNP Westminster leader Stephen Flynn
OL,8,Fhas written to Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,9,FStarmer to call for a four-nation
OL,10,Fsummit on tackling child poverty this
OL,11,Fsummer.
OL,13,FMr Flynn welcomed news the UK
OL,14,FGovernment has set up a ministerial
OL,15,Ftaskforce to kick-start its child
OL,16,Fpoverty strategy, and said it should
OL,17,Fnot delay action on the issue.
