OL,3,CFour-nation summit needed now to
OL,4,Ctackle child poverty, says Stephen
OL,5,CFlynn
OL,7,FHe confirmed the SNP will press ahead
OL,8,Fwith its amendment to the King's
OL,9,FSpeech calling for the two-child
OL,10,Fbenefit cap to be scrapped
OL,11,Fimmediately, with a vote on it
OL,12,Fexpected to take place next week.
OL,14,FIn his letter, Mr Flynn said
OL,15,FWestminster cuts and Brexit had seen
OL,16,Fthe UK become "one of the poorest and
OL,17,Fmost unequal countries among our
OL,18,FEuropean neighbours".
