OL,3,CFour-nation summit needed now to
OL,4,Ctackle child poverty, says Stephen
OL,5,CFlynn
OL,7,FHe added: "That will only change with
OL,8,Fconcerted action and substantial
OL,9,Finvestment from the UK Government,
OL,10,Fwhich has been severely lacking. The
OL,11,Ftaskforce must not be used as an
OL,12,Fexcuse to delay action.
OL,14,F"Scrapping the cap is the bare minimum
OL,15,Frequired if your Government wants to
OL,16,Fscratch the surface on tackling child
OL,17,Fpoverty, and every day you delay, more
OL,18,Fchildren will suffer the consequences
OL,19,Fof Labour Government inaction.
