OL,3,CFour-nation summit needed now to
OL,4,Ctackle child poverty, says Stephen
OL,5,CFlynn
OL,7,F"It is important for the governments
OL,8,Facross the isles to work together on
OL,9,Fthis issue, to move quickly and to
OL,10,Flearn from best practice. I am
OL,11,Ftherefore calling for a four-nations
OL,12,Fsummit on eradicating child poverty
OL,13,Fthis summer.
OL,15,F"I also think it's vital that parties
OL,16,Facross Parliament get the opportunity
OL,17,Fto feed into the taskforce."
