OL,3,CFour-nation summit needed now to
OL,4,Ctackle child poverty, says Stephen
OL,5,CFlynn
OL,7,FThe SNP says a package of measures is
OL,8,Fneeded to tackle child poverty,
OL,9,Fincluding matching the Scottish
OL,10,FGovernment's Scottish child payment by
OL,11,Fraising universal credit by #26.70 per
OL,12,Fchild, per week across the UK.
OL,14,FWith Scottish Labour leader Anas
OL,15,FSarwar among those to have spoken out
OL,16,Fagainst the two-child benefit cap, Mr
OL,17,FFlynn challenged the party's MPs from
OL,18,FScotland to back his amendment.
