OL,3,CFour-nation summit needed now to
OL,4,Ctackle child poverty, says Stephen
OL,5,CFlynn
OL,7,FIf selected, the amendment will go to
OL,8,Fa vote next week, with Mr Flynn
OL,9,Finsisting: "It's shameful that Keir
OL,10,FStarmer has made the political choice
OL,11,Fto continue imposing Tory austerity
OL,12,Fcuts, instead of delivering the change
OL,13,Fthat people in Scotland were promised."
OL,15,FThe policy was introduced by the
OL,16,FConservatives in 2017 and prevents
OL,17,Ffamilies claiming Universal Credit or
OL,18,Fchild tax credits for a third child,
OL,19,Fexcept in very limited circumstances.
