OL,3,CFour-nation summit needed now to
OL,4,Ctackle child poverty, says Stephen
OL,5,CFlynn
OL,7,FResponding to Mr Flynn's comments, a
OL,8,FUK Government spokesman said: "As the
OL,9,FPM has made clear, no child should be
OL,10,Fin poverty and the Government is
OL,11,Fcommitted to developing an ambitious
OL,12,Fstrategy to reduce child poverty and
OL,13,Fgive children the best start in life.
OL,15,F"The new ministerial taskforce will
OL,16,Fexplore how we can use all the
OL,17,Favailable levers across Government to
OL,18,Fcreate an ambitious strategy, and we
OL,19,Fwill continue to work closely with all
OL,20,Fof the devolved governments as we
OL,21,Fbring forward this urgent work."
